data.description: MLS# 14673755 - Built by HistoryMaker Homes - November completion! ~ This Beautiful brand new home with an open concept design provides enormous space and functionality. Master suite includes double walk in closets, additional sitting area, and more! Master bath includes dual vanities and large 5 foot walk in shower. The secondary bedrooms are huge and also feature large walk in closets. 42 inch white Cabinets, Kitchen Island, Recess lighting. This home is has a smart, comfortable flow that is sure to impress! Van Alstyne is conveniently located off 75 just north of McKinney and has A rated schools. Get a brand new home at an affordable price in a great school district. Photos are representative.
